title: Mark Gimenez - The Governor's Wife (Retail)
description:
Mark Gimenez - The Governor's Wife - Retail (epub)


A Texas governor wants to be president . . . his wife wants to escape his suffocating ambition . . . and a Mexican drug lord wants him dead.

When the drug lord abducts the governor's wife while she is working secretly as a nurse in a colonia on the border, Governor Bode Bonner must choose between his wife and the White House, between his life and hers.
